+        # Cache of the last commanded gimbal pan/tilt (degrees). The Waveshare pan-tilt board
+        # uses open-loop PWM servos with no encoder feedback -- the ESP32's T=1001 telemetry
+        # `pan`/`tilt` fields are frozen at magic values and do NOT track actual servo
+        # position. Instead we cache the most recent /gimbal/absolute command and republish
+        # it as /gimbal/state. After one servo settle-time (~300ms for a 90deg move at
+        # speed=600) the commanded position is effectively the actual position.
+        # Initialized to (0, 0) so subscribers get a sane default before any command lands.
+        self._last_gimbal_pan = 0.0
